<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>국내 시사 퀴즈</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 14px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .stat-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .stat { background: #f5f5f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 0.8rem; text-align: center; }
    .stat-val { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 2px; }
    button.primary {
      width: 100%; padding: 13px; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff;
      border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    button.primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    .progress-bar { background: #eee; border-radius: 4px; height: 5px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .progress-fill { background: #1a1a1a; height: 5px; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 0.3s; }
    .meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .question-box {
      background: #f9f9f7; border: 1px solid #e8e8e4; border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .options { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .opt-btn {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left;
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .opt-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #f5f5f0; border-color: #bbb; }
    .opt-btn.correct { background: #e8f5e9; border-color: #4caf50; color: #2e7d32; }
    .opt-btn.wrong { background: #fce4ec; border-color: #e57373; color: #c62828; }
    .opt-btn:disabled { cursor: default; }
    .feedback {
      margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; display: none;
    }
    .feedback.correct { background: #e8f5e9; border: 1px solid #a5d6a7; color: #2e7d32; }
    .feedback.wrong { background: #fce4ec; border: 1px solid #f48fb1; color: #c62828; }
    .feedback .expl { color: #555; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
    button.next-btn {
      display: none; width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 12px;
      background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer;
    }
    button.next-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    .result-emoji { font-size: 48px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .result-text { font-size: 15px; color: #555; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .hidden { display: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <div id="start-screen">
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <div style="font-size:40px; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">📰</div>
      <h1>국내 시사 퀴즈</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">매번 랜덤으로 출제되는 국내 시사 문제</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-row">
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val">5</div><div class="stat-label">문제</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val">4지선다</div><div class="stat-label">형식</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val">랜덤</div><div class="stat-label">문제 출제</div></div>
    </div>
    <button class="primary" onclick="startGame()">게임 시작 →</button>
  </div>

  <div id="quiz-screen" class="hidden">
    <div class="meta">
      <span id="q-num"></span>
      <span id="score-display"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div></div>
    <div class="question-box" id="q-text"></div>
    <div class="options" id="options-container"></div>
    <div class="feedback" id="feedback"></div>
    <button class="next-btn" id="next-btn" onclick="nextQuestion()">다음 문제 →</button>
  </div>

  <div id="result-screen" class="hidden">
    <div class="result-emoji" id="result-emoji"></div>
    <p class="result-text" id="result-text"></p>
    <div class="stat-row">
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val" id="r-score"></div><div class="stat-label">점수</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val" id="r-correct"></div><div class="stat-label">정답</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val" id="r-grade"></div><div class="stat-label">등급</div></div>
    </div>
    <button class="primary" onclick="startGame()">↺ 다시 하기</button>
  </div>

</div>

